metadata.name: Tiny Owl 1
metadata.description:
Congrats summoner! You just evoked a 'Tiny Owl' - A nocturnal spirit who likes to fly under the moonlight and rest on ancient magical relics. He/She is now going to be your companion for the rest of your journey! 

There are only 100 of them in total and they are all special as we designed, painted and sculpted them one by one with lots of love
